(333, 1, '2014-06-26 15:30:47', '2014-06-26 15:30:47', 'Simply changing the pattern of cutting a field will allow animals an escape route from mowing equipment. Instead of starting your cut along the perimeter of the field, instead consider starting in the centre and working outwards, or going back and forth starting at one side of the field.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/farming/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mowing-patterns.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-334 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/farming/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mowing-patterns-300x145.png" alt="mowing-patterns" width="300" height="145" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Mowing in Different Patterns', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', '333-2', '', '', '2014-06-26 15:31:14', '2014-06-26 15:31:14', '', 317, 'http://localhost/farming/?page_id=333', 0, 'page', '', 0),
